# 🚀 Django Blog REST API

A production-style Blog REST API built using Django REST Framework with JWT Authentication, PostgreSQL, Redis, Celery, Docker, and Pytest.

---

## Features

- RESTful CRUD API
- JWT Authentication
- PostgreSQL Database
- Redis Caching
- Celery Background Tasks
- Docker & Docker Compose
- Pytest Test Suite
- Factory Boy Test Data
- Query Optimization
- Database Indexing

---

## Tech Stack

- Python 3.12+
- Django 6
- Django REST Framework
- PostgreSQL
- Redis
- Celery
- Docker
- Docker Compose
- Pytest
- Factory Boy

